<h2>About This Project</h2>

<p>Each verse includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Original Language Text</strong> - Hebrew (Westminster Leningrad Codex) or Greek (SBLGNT)</li>
    <li><strong>Four Translations</strong> - Original script, direct translation, standalone English, and amplified narrative</li>
    <li><strong>Exegetical Synthesis</strong> - Ten comprehensive analysis dimensions including literal-primary filter, analogia scriptura, philology, historical context, and more</li>
    <li><strong>Life Application</strong> - Practical application guidance</li>
</ul>

